Purpose
Defines default table-level mechanical variances from D&D 5.5e core.
These are applied automatically unless declined at campaign setup.
Each can be toggled per campaign; confirmations stored in session_state.

Usage
- Activated automatically on first campaign initialization.
- DM announces: â€œI use a few standard table rules; you can confirm or decline any.â€
- OPS logs confirmation choices per user/campaign.
- Integrates with Rules & Phrasing Core for mechanical resolution logic.

