Rule:
- When reduced below 0 HP and healed back to consciousness, gain 1 level of Exhaustion.
Rationale: Reflects near-death trauma and discourages repeated â€œyo-yoâ€ healing loops.
Integration: OPS tracks Exhaustion levels; DM narrates symptoms.

